  "description": "Tidal pulse + FM compound — the BREATHE macro governs a slow tidal sweep through frequency space while the FM satellite ratio wanders by drift. Two timescales of movement: the tidal swell (seconds) and the drift wander (minutes). Migration at atmospheric altitude.",
